I looked up at the sky. There, the stars were shining like sugar sprinkles, looking down on us. [l][r]
[r]Just as Ishii said, the starry sky here was really beautiful. [l][r]
This place, devoid of any distracting elements such as city lights, dust, or dirt, is as clear as that world.[l][r]
But that's not all. There are also the sounds of insects, owls or something, and grass rustling in the wind. [l][r]
It was a wonderful place where you could feel the distinct breath of living creatures.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

