"Yu, can you see it?" [l][r]

[r]I pushed my wheelchair to the middle of the grassland and squatted down next to Yu.
Hmm. Maybe because I'm late for our meeting again today, he didn't reply. [l][r]

[r]But then, all I have to do is wait. And I will continue to call and wait. [l][r]

[r]This is the best way to make up for the mistakes I made. [l][r]

Until you wake up. Because I decided to stay with you until you come back here. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
"Look. It's beautiful, isn't it? It's like the stars are falling. You said the same thing, didn't you?" [l][r]
[r]The wind blew. The grass and trees swayed and began to chatter. There was certainly life here. But it seemed like there were only two of us in this world, and it was very quiet. [l][r]
I thought that it must be the whole world. [l][r]
"At that time, I felt like I was one with the world, and I knew you felt the same way.[l][r]
…I’m sorry for saying ‘you’. The truth is, I was really happy.”[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
Yes, it's the same. This sky, the air I breathe, and the earth I walk on. [l][r]
Everything, every single one of them, is the whole of the world. [l][r]
[r]It's the same whether the world is over or the world is now. [l][r]
Of course, I and you are part of this world, and we are everything. [l][r]
[r]So it's not painful. I can wait forever [r]
Because my very existence is also proof of your existence. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

